author: Business Insider
description:
Sponsored by UK Export Finance

Ama Amo-Agyei, founder of Plantmade, launched her plant-based haircare business with only £100 and quickly expanded internationally, exporting to markets like the US, Nigeria, and Ghana. She shares the challenges of securing financing as a Black entrepreneur and how UK Export Finance (UKEF) helps businesses to access working capital and manage the risks of not getting paid by offering a government guarantee.
